---
/** Four-layer stack — maps to service pillars order. */
---
<div class="lp-viz lp-chart-stack" data-viz>
  <div class="lp-viz-head">
    <p class="lp-viz-kicker">Architecture</p>
    <p class="lp-viz-title">How the layers stack</p>
    <p class="lp-viz-note">Nothing in visibility or conversion moves until positioning and narrative define what must be true for revenue.</p>
  </div>
  <ol class="lp-stack-list" role="list">
    <li class="lp-stack-item" style="--i: 0">
      <span class="lp-stack-num">04</span>
      <div class="lp-stack-copy">
        <span class="lp-stack-label">Conversion infrastructure</span>
        <span class="lp-stack-hint">Bridge from “seen” to “signed”</span>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="lp-stack-item" style="--i: 1">
      <span class="lp-stack-num">03</span>
      <div class="lp-stack-copy">
        <span class="lp-stack-label">Visibility architecture</span>
        <span class="lp-stack-hint">Every asset earns its place</span>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="lp-stack-item" style="--i: 2">
      <span class="lp-stack-num">02</span>
      <div class="lp-stack-copy">
        <span class="lp-stack-label">Narrative & messaging</span>
        <span class="lp-stack-hint">What the market repeats about you</span>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="lp-stack-item lp-stack-item--base" style="--i: 3">
      <span class="lp-stack-num">01</span>
      <div class="lp-stack-copy">
        <span class="lp-stack-label">Strategic positioning</span>
        <span class="lp-stack-hint">Blueprint — nothing moves without it</span>
      </div>
    </li>
  </ol>
</div>
